Calling `a.prop` and `a.refs` is UB, because parent `objbase` was *not constructed correctly*. I've had a hard time to figure out what is wrong with this bindings (can you see it?).

Yes -- I've forgot to mention `iface` in template args list of `class_<mytype, ...`. OK, let's fix that:
